LABEL: SQ01
en-US: Survey Question 1.

LABEL: surveygreet
en-US: Thanks for participating in our survey.  Using a scale from 1 to 5, where 1 is poor and 5 is great, please rate us on the following questions.

LABEL: surveyend
en-US: Your survey results have been saved.  Thanks for participating!

LABEL: surveyerror
en-US: There was an error processing your survey responses.

LABEL: closed
en-US: Our office is currently closed.  Our operating hours are from 8 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.  If you would like to leave a voice message, please press 1.

LABEL: holiday
en-US: Today is a holiday and our office is currently closed.  If you would like to leave a voice message, please press 1.

LABEL: monitor
en-US: Your call may be monitored or recorded to help improve our services.

LABEL: noagents
en-US: We’re sorry, at this time, there are no agents available to take your call.  If you would like to leave a voice message, please press 1.

LABEL: pleasehold
en-US: Please hold while we transfer you to an agent.

LABEL: busy
en-US: All agents are currently assisting other callers. Please hold for the next available agent.

LABEL: highvolume
en-US: We are experiencing unusually high call volumes and extended hold times. Please hold for the next available agent.

LABEL: stillbusy
en-US: All agents are still currently assisting other callers. Please hold for the next available agent. If you would like to leave a message, please press 1. To speak to the next available agent press 8 or remain on the line.

LABEL: voicemail
en-US: Please leave a message after the tone.

LABEL: saved
en-US: Your message has been saved. An agent will return your call as soon as possible.

LABEL: goodbye
en-US: Thank you for calling. Goodbye.

LABEL: difficulties
en-US: We apologize, we’re experiencing technical difficulties and cannot take your call at this time. Please try again later.

LABEL: InvalidInput1
en-US: That was an invalid selection. Please try again

LABEL: InvalidInput2
en-US: Sorry, that choice is still invalid. Please try again.

LABEL: NoInput1
en-US: We did not receive your entry. Please try again.

LABEL: NoInput2
en-US: We still did not receive your entry.  Please try again.

LABEL: MaxInputXfer
en-US: Sorry, we're still having trouble.

LABEL: enterID
en-US: Please enter your identification number.

LABEL: youentered
en-US: You entered

LABEL: confirmentry
en-US: If this is correct, press 1.  Otherwise, press 2.
